elements.name: Como usuario me registro y creo un nuevo tag con una imagen

steps.name: I enter to the setup page v "<SETUP_VALUES_REMOTE>" and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "1"
I click in the tags menu button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "2"
I click in the new tag button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "3"
I fill the tag name "<TAG_NAME>" v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "4"
I click in the add image to tag v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "5"
I click the save tag button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "6"
I click in the tags menu button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "7"
I verify the tag name created is "<TAG_NAME>" v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-tag" scenario "2" step "8"
